## Sign-Out Scopes — Controlling Which Devices Are Signed Out

```typescript
// Sign out this device only (default)
await supabase.auth.signOut({ scope: 'local' })

// Sign out ALL devices (account compromise response)
await supabase.auth.signOut({ scope: 'global' })

// Sign out all OTHER devices (keep current session)
await supabase.auth.signOut({ scope: 'others' })
```

```typescript
// "Sign out all devices" button in settings
export async function POST() {
  const supabase = await createClient()
  await supabase.auth.signOut({ scope: 'global' })
  return NextResponse.redirect('/login')
}
```

