## Session Lifecycle Controls (Pro plan)

```
Dashboard → Auth → Sessions

Settings:
  Time-box sessions: ON/OFF
    → Forces re-login after X days regardless of activity
    → Default: OFF (sessions never expire)

  Inactivity timeout: X hours
    → Signs out user if no activity for X hours
    → Default: OFF

  Single session per user: ON/OFF
    → Signing in on device 2 revokes device 1
    → Default: OFF (multiple concurrent sessions allowed)
```

